dict.string: Get and format all macro-related UUID stuff

set apscDone1 to false set loopCount1 to 0 repeat until apscDone1 is true or loopCount1 is 15 try -- Initialize lists set idList to {} set UUIDList to {} set NameList to {} set StatusList to {} -- Get all macros tell application "Keyboard Maestro" set macroCount to count macros repeat with i from 1 to macroCount set thisMacro to macro i set end of idList to id of macro group of thisMacro set end of UUIDList to id of thisMacro set end of NameList to name of thisMacro set end of StatusList to enabled of thisMacro end repeat end tell -- Combine the lists set combinedList to {} set itemCount to (count of idList) repeat with i from 1 to itemCount set combinedItem to item i of idList & "‚Üêüî∏‚Üí" & item i of UUIDList & "‚Üêüî∏‚Üí" & item i of NameList & "‚Üêüî∏‚Üí" & item i of StatusList set end of combinedList to combinedItem end repeat -- Convert the combined list to text set AppleScript's text item delimiters to linefeed set combinedText to combinedList as text set kmInst to system attribute "KMINSTANCE" tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine" setvariable "instance_UUIDmacros" instance kmInst to (combinedList as text) end tell set apscDone1 to true on error set apscDone1 to false set loopCount1 to loopCount1 + 1 end try end repeat

Get and format all group-related UUID stuff

set apscDone1 to false set loopCount1 to 0 repeat until apscDone1 is true or loopCount1 is 15 try --if application "Keyboard Maestro Engine" is not running then tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine" to launch tell application "Keyboard Maestro" set groupUUID to get id of macro groups set groupName to get name of macro groups set groupStatus to get enabled of macro groups end tell set combinedList to {} repeat with i from 1 to count of groupUUID set groupUUIDText to (item i of groupUUID) as text set groupNameText to (item i of groupName) as text set groupStatusText to (item i of groupStatus) as text set combinedRecord to groupUUIDText & "‚Üêüî∏‚Üí" & groupNameText & "‚Üêüî∏‚Üí" & groupStatusText & linefeed set end of combinedList to combinedRecord end repeat set kmInst to system attribute "KMINSTANCE" tell application "Keyboard Maestro Engine" setvariable "instance_UUIDgroups" instance kmInst to (combinedList as text) end tell set apscDone1 to true on error set apscDone1 to false set loopCount1 to loopCount1 + 1 end try end repeat
